# Playground galleries three-layer boundary — IDE anti-drift contract

**Canonical decision:** [ADR-0035](../../docs/decisions/0035-three-layer-surface-ide-anti-drift.md) (AGENTS.md **PRIORITY #2**) · Layer 1 seal: [`app/(main)/[locale]/playground/_SEAL.md`](../../app/(main)/[locale]/playground/_SEAL.md)

**If this rule and `AGENTS.md` diverge, follow `AGENTS.md` and fix this rule in the same PR.**

Local developer galleries use **one product name everywhere: `playground`**.

Mechanical guard: [`tests/unit/playground-surface-contract.test.ts`](../../tests/unit/playground-surface-contract.test.ts)

---

## Prime directive

```txt
Layer 1 — app/           → URL + thin re-exports ONLY
Layer 2 — lib/features/  → playground gate, fixtures, page orchestrators
Layer 3 — components2/   → gallery client islands ONLY (overlays → components2/dev/)
```

**Import doors:**

| Layer | Door |
| --- | --- |
| Layer 2 | `#features/playground` · `#features/playground/server` |
| Layer 3 (galleries) | `#components2/playground/*` |
| Client fixtures/paths | `#features/playground/client` |

---

## Layer 1 — `app/.../playground/`

**Allowed in leaf `page.tsx`:**

```tsx
export { PlaygroundShellPreviewPage as default } from "#features/playground/server"
```

**Forbidden:** `AppShell` wiring, gallery fixtures, `redirectIfProductionPlaygroundRoute`, `#components2/playground` in routes.

---

## Layer 2 — `lib/features/playground/`

**Owns:** `NODE_ENV` gallery gate, validated fixtures, RSC page bodies.

| Concern | Path |
| --- | --- |
| Playground route gate | `data/playground-route-gate.server.ts` |
| Playground href constants | `schemas/playground-paths.shared.ts` |
| Renderer fixtures | `data/gallery-fixtures.ts`, `data/gallery-scenarios.ts` |
| Pattern C fixtures | `data/pattern-c-gallery-fixtures.ts` |
| Shell preview fixtures | `data/shell-preview-fixtures/*` |
| Page orchestrators | `components/playground-*-page.server.tsx`, `playground-gated-gallery-page.server.tsx` |

**Forbidden at module root:** `_SEAL.md`

---

## Layer 3 — `components2/playground/`

**Owns:** client preview frames, shell preview client mocks.

**May import:** `#features/playground/client`, `#components2/ui/*`, `#app-shell/client`.

**Forbidden:** server barrel `#features/playground/server`, gallery scenario registries, production redirect gate.

**`index.ts` door:** fixtures + `playground-paths.shared` only — **not** RSC page exports (use `#features/playground/server` in routes).

**NODE_ENV overlays** (`route-error-debug-panel`, `dev-signin-panel`) stay in `components2/dev/`.

---

## Verification

```bash
pnpm lint:path -- lib/features/playground components2/playground
pnpm test:fast -- tests/unit/playground-surface-contract.test.ts
pnpm typecheck
```
